      <b data-is-speakable>This Diet Is Better For the Planet. But Is It Better For You, Too?  : The Salt</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Less than a half-ounce of red meat per day: That's how much a new report says we should eat to meet nutritional needs and help save the planet. Americans on average now eat four to six times as much.</b>
